==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: force-feed
<hw>force-feed</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to feed (someone) against his
will, as during a hunger strike.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>force-feed</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: force-feed
<hw>force-feed</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a method of lubricating internal
combustion engines in which a pump forces oil into the engine
bearings.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> lubricating system, force-feed lubricating system,
force feed, pressure-feed lubricating system, pressure feed.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forceful</ent>⟦br⟧
